{"tid":1341714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[對警戰術策略整合] 12點前不散，無限勇武，自制煙彈","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:58:39.000Z","uid":771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4443a494e14e797fe8ae88c85422dea3c48791","tid":1341714,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"盾，棍，大量和理非守後守路障<br />\n<br />\n今日發夢10點尾見到有五至六部警車係ifc 想衝去上環包抄<br />\n<br />\n但佢地係隧道仔未上到地面就發現上面果部和理非守緊勇武後方<br />\n<br />\n完全無包抄既可能<br />\n<br />\n12點後少左和理非人數，勇武就應該退場<br />\n<br />\n下次可以搵目標黎攻<br />\n<br />\n4-8pm 無限勇武<br />\n<br />\n各位武運亨通，我覺得今日政總其實可以攻下，睇下拆水馬要幾耐"},{"pid":"0c3d94d239727dd568b6b8c182a246b014cbd6ff","tid":1341714,"uid":70650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acee34c55c5a75a7e1c7da50737acd0c3702f486","tid":1341714,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:58:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}